                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "value": ", and stripping input prompts from code blocks. This functionality   was duplicated in "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "inlineCode",
                      "value": "IPython.core.inputsplitter"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "value": ", and the latter version   was already what IPython relied on. A new API to transform input will be ready   before release."
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
